case 1278: if(playerHasItem(1351) || playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == 1351) { startAnimation(879); addItem(1511, 1); addSkillXP(1000, 8); sendMessage("You get some logs."); ReplaceObject2(objectX, objectY, 1342, 0, 10); break; } else { sendMessage("You need an axe to cut this tree!"); } break;
